The sandbox-exec module runs Python scripts in the Monty sandbox —
the same environment as /exec in nanalogue-chat — with no LLM involved.

Resource limits (max-records, max-duration, max-memory, etc.) are shared
with nanalogue-chat through sandbox-cli-args.ts so they stay in sync.
